ComponentService --> ComponentEntity : uses
ComponentService --> ComponentRepo : uses
TemplateService --> TemplateEntity : uses
TemplateService --> TemplateRepo : uses
TemplateCommandService --> TemplateEntity : uses
TemplateCommandService --> TemplateRepo : uses
DataBindingService --> DataSourceEntity : uses
DataBindingService --> DataSourceRepo : uses
DataSourceService --> DataSourceEntity : uses
DataSourceService --> DataSourceRepo : uses
DataSourceStructureService --> DataSourceEntity : uses
JsonHelperService --> DataSourceEntity : process
CanvasService --> ComponentFactory : uses
SchemaExportService --> SchemaEntity : uses
SchemaExportService --> PersistenceManager : uses
SchemaImportService --> SchemaEntity : uses
SchemaImportService --> PersistenceManager : uses
SchemaRenderer --> SchemaEntity : uses
SchemaRenderer --> ComponentService : uses

AIGeneratorAdapter --> AIGeneratorPackage : uses
AIGeneratorAdapter --> TemplateService : uses (see adapter)

AIGeneratorPackage --> ComponentGenerator : uses
AIGeneratorPackage --> PageGenerator : uses
AIGeneratorPackage --> ComponentValidator : uses
AIGeneratorPackage --> PageValidator : uses
AIGeneratorPackage --> PromptBuilders : uses
AIGeneratorPackage --> JsonParser : uses
