VisualEditor --> CDNService : load static
SchemaRenderer --> CDNService : load static

note right of VisualEditor
  **Main flows:**
  1. Components → services → domain → stores → local/DB
  2. Data delta → state → collaboration
  3. JSON → JSON svc → datasource → binding → renderers
  4. Datasource pick → service → parse → render
  5. Schema export → svc → processor → persistence → files
  6. Schema import → svc → processor → persistence → state
  7. Schema render → renderer → component svc → canvas
  8. CSV/XML → datasource svc → parser → binding
  9. Mapping → binding → mapper → renderers
  10. Layout → canvas svc → calculator → move
  11. Forms → template cmd → template → renderers
  12. State persist → manager → adapters → storage
  13. AI component chain → canvas
  14. AI page chain → canvas
end note

@enduml

